        "title": "feat: add Hide critters menu bar option",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nFixes #1563.\n\nAdds a Display setting that removes provider-specific faces and decorations from menu-bar quota bars while preserving the meter fills. The preference defaults off and repaints merged, per-provider, and morph icons immediately.\n\n## Implementation\n\n- Persist Hide critters in Settings and include it in menu observation.\n- Gate Codex, Claude, Gemini, Antigravity, Factory, and Warp decorations in IconRenderer.\n- Include the preference in static and morph cache keys and render signatures.\n- Route it through every live menu-bar and menu icon path.\n- Localize the setting in every app language.\n- Cover persistence, observation, caches, morphs, every decorated style, undecorated styles, and Warp without a weekly quota.\n\n## Verification\n\nExact candidate: 9a6fe7c3b29e15c1995a3ff86d29ac51ea7d6d24\n\n- 76 focused tests passed.\n- make check passed with zero format or lint findings.\n- Exact rebased-head Codex autoreview: no accepted/actionable findings, confidence 0.84.\n- Exact rebased-head ad-hoc package completed; deep strict code-sign verification passed; bundle reports `CodexGitCommit=9a6fe7c3`.\n- Exact-size 546 x 662 Display-pane renders verified English and long German labels without clipping.\n- Live Settings capture was attempted; macOS App Data consent blocks synthetic interaction on this machine. Existing contributor screenshots below demonstrate the unchanged before/after runtime behavior.\n\n## Screenshots\n\nBefore:\n\n<img width=\"550\" height=\"752\" alt=\"Settings before enabling Hide critters\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c1d1c9b8-441a-4fca-8871-c18514fa16fc\" />\n<img width=\"103\" height=\"37\" alt=\"Decorated menu bar meters\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5659ff29-7a26-461b-bedb-1070f74e39e1\" />\n\nAfter:\n\n<img width=\"550\" height=\"753\" alt=\"Settings after enabling Hide critters\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/cb0e9f00-31af-4439-8f0c-52d3a0c12983\" />\n<img width=\"97\" height=\"34\" alt=\"Plain menu bar meters\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3811aa1f-094e-45b2-886b-6d67dc532c89\" />\n",
